experiment-order-ame-name = Overloaded AME Scanning
experiment-order-ame-desc = Our partners at Nakamura Engineering request telemetry from an AME controller operating injection above safe threshold, to improve their future antimatter engine models.

experiment-order-species-safe-name = Study of Reagent Effects on Species
experiment-order-species-safe-desc = Scan a subject of species: { $species }, containing reagent { $reagent } in their bloodstream, so we can better study its effects on this species.

experiment-order-species-unsafe-name = Study of Hazardous Reagent Effects on Species
experiment-order-species-unsafe-desc = Scan a subject of species: { $species }, containing hazardous reagent { $reagent } in their bloodstream, so we can better study its effects on this species. Reminder: the subject must sign a liability waiver before the experiment.

experiment-order-vomit-name = Vomit Composition Collection
experiment-order-vomit-desc = We are looking for the most effective way to combat vomiting to reduce cleaning costs. To do this, we need to collect data from scanning any vomit puddle.

experiment-order-ripley-name = Ripley Mech Collection
experiment-order-ripley-desc = Assemble a Ripley mech with 3 modules, then transfer it to the Supply department. Provide a scan of the fully equipped Ripley mech as proof.

experiment-order-pet-name = Department Pet Scanning
experiment-order-pet-desc = Due to increasing cases of animal abuse at our facilities, we are gathering information on station animals. Today's pet to scan: { $target }.

experiment-order-xeno-name = Fauna Scanning
experiment-order-xeno-desc = A field scan of xenobiological species: { $target } is required, so we can better study this fauna species.

experiment-order-vending-name = Vending Machine Usage Statistics
experiment-order-vending-desc = We are collecting usage statistics for items from: { $target } in the { $department } department. Scan it, then repeat the scan after 10 minutes.

experiment-order-meat-name = Food Quality Assessment (Meat)
experiment-order-meat-desc = One of our top chefs requires 5 scans of meat dishes so they can improve their meat dish recipes. Provide a series of 5 scans of meat dishes, excluding the standard fried steak.

experiment-order-id-name = Study of Microwave Effects on ID Cards
experiment-order-id-desc = Provide us with a scan of an ID card after thermal exposure in a microwave oven.

experiment-order-baton-name = Stun Baton and Plasma Experiment
experiment-order-baton-desc = We are investigating the effects of liquid plasma on energy carriers. For this, we need a scan of a stun baton containing at least 5u of plasma in its battery.

experiment-order-seed-name = GMO Plant Study
experiment-order-seed-desc = For plant genome research, we require a scan of: { $target }.

experiment-order-radcollector-name = Radiation Collector Reading Scan
experiment-order-radcollector-desc = Take readings from a radiation collector under a load of at least 6 rad.

experiment-order-canister-gas-name = Chemical Gas Research
experiment-order-canister-gas-desc = To confirm one of our scientific theories, provide a scan of a canister containing at least 500 moles of gas: { $gas }.

experiment-order-captain-id-name = Captain ID Card Scanning
experiment-order-captain-id-desc = Some dishonest Acting-Captains spoil spare captain cards. Scan a Captain's ID card to assist us in our further investigation.

experiment-order-weapon-name = Defective Weapon Batch Search
experiment-order-weapon-desc = A recent batch of weapons delivered to our facilities turned out to be defective. Scan one of: { $target }, so we can verify that there is no defective weaponry on your station.

experiment-order-paper-signatures-name = Signature Database Update
experiment-order-paper-signatures-desc = We update our employee databases monthly. Submit a scan of a document containing signatures from at least five different individuals.

experiment-order-bible-name = Holy Book Scanning
experiment-order-bible-desc = We require a scan of any holy book.

experiment-order-fruit-dishes-name = Food Analysis (Fruit)
experiment-order-fruit-dishes-desc = We are looking for the fruit dish richest in vitamins. Prepare and scan 3 fruit dishes for the culinary sample.

experiment-order-soups-name = Food Analysis (Soups)
experiment-order-soups-desc = One of our top chefs requires 5 scans of soups so they can improve their recipes. Provide a series of 5 scans of soups.

experiment-order-gravity-name = Gravity Field Measurement
experiment-order-gravity-desc = A scan of a functional and active gravity generator is required for our report.

experiment-order-combat-mech-name = Combat Mech Construction
experiment-order-combat-mech-desc = Assemble a { $target } mech with 3 modules, then transfer it to the Security department. Provide a scan of the fully equipped mech as proof.

experiment-order-material-name = Material Formula Scanning
experiment-order-material-desc = A reference scan of a material of category: { $target } is required.